Q: Which sector had the lowest volatility last year?
A: SELECT a.sector, AVG(f.vol_30) AS avg_vol FROM fact_market_data f JOIN dim_asset a ON f.asset_key = a.asset_key JOIN dim_date d ON f.date_key = d.date_key WHERE d.year = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) - 1 GROUP BY a.sector ORDER BY avg_vol ASC LIMIT 1;

Q: Which stock had the highest close price last month?
A: SELECT a.ticker, MAX(f.close) AS max_close FROM fact_market_data f JOIN dim_asset a ON f.asset_key = a.asset_key JOIN dim_date d ON f.date_key = d.date_key WHERE d.month = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 month') AND d.year = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 month') GROUP BY a.ticker ORDER BY max_close DESC LIMIT 1;

Q: What is the average news count per ticker?
A: SELECT a.ticker, AVG(f.news_count) AS avg_news FROM fact_market_data f JOIN dim_asset a ON f.asset_key = a.asset_key GROUP BY a.ticker ORDER BY avg_news DESC;

